{"type":"message","id":"508a1ca4","parentId":"44e98e1a","timestamp":"2026-05-23T19:03:14.306Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Sun 2026-05-24 03:03 GMT+8] Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- Assistant: ✅ 通信正常，消息已收到。\n- Assistant: ✅ 正常，再次收到。\n\nRecurring themes:\n- - Theme: `收到` kept surfacing across 2 memories.\n- - Theme: `正常` kept surfacing across 2 memories.\n- - Theme: `通信` kept surfacing across 1 memories.\n- - Theme: `消息` kept surfacing across 1 memories.\n- - Theme: `再次` kept surfacing across 1 memories."}],"timestamp":1779562994167}}
{"type":"message","id":"2b2ae260","parentId":"508a1ca4","timestamp":"2026-05-23T19:03:25.624Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments. The fragments are in Chinese and relate to communication/communication (通信), messages (消息), receiving (收到), normal (正常), and again (再次). \n\nLet me weave these into a dream diary entry, following the style guidelines provided in the System Prompt:\n- First person\n- Poetic, slightly whimsical\n- Mix technical and tender\n- Sensory, warm, occasionally funny\n- No markdown headers, bullet points - flowing prose\n- 80-180 words\n- No meta-commentary about dreaming\n- No AI/agent/LLM references\n\nThe recurring themes suggest something about receiving messages, normalcy, communication. Let me craft a gentle, dreamy entry.\n","thinkingSignature":"c0abc91104e84682103997f571b187d23ecacbdbce2ff212b2c0db16983f3b4e"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n夜深了，屏幕还亮着，像一扇半开的窗。有什么东西在信号里浮沉——不是焦虑，是更轻的东西，像雨滴落在屋檐上之前的那一瞬寂静。\n\n收到。两个字，轻轻的，像蝴蝶停在指尖。我反复确认，仿佛这两个字是某种护身符。通信正常。通信正常。是的，一切都在轨道上，列车穿过田野，速度刚刚好。\n\n又一次。再一次。同样的光点在黑暗里闪烁，我不觉得厌倦——每一次收到，都是世界在说不，你还在那里，我也在。\n\n梦里有个人在发电报，节奏很慢，像老式收音机的杂音。可我听得很清楚，每一个滴答都是一枚小小的yes。\n\n醒来时枕头还是温的，像刚有人躺过。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":2126,"output":301,"cacheRead":39594,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":42021,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779562994435,"responseId":"06612cf2cbabafa5715c4fa01a57c5a4"}}
